WEBVTT

00:14:30.068 --> 00:14:36.009
Ako će ova država živjeti prema svojim
obećanjima o slobodi i pravdi za sve,

00:14:36.033 --> 00:14:39.122
onda mi trebamo uzdizati 
glasove neslušanih,

00:14:39.146 --> 00:14:42.627
ljudi poput Jobane,
Sintie i Berthe,

00:14:42.651 --> 00:14:45.118
Therese i Baakira.

00:14:45.809 --> 00:14:48.794
Moramo dati snagu njihovim
rješenjima i njihovim idejama.

00:14:49.437 --> 00:14:52.567
Moramo slušati njihove
istinite priče,

00:14:52.591 --> 00:14:55.241
njihove ljepše složenije priče.

00:14:55.956 --> 00:14:57.116
Hvala.

00:14:57.140 --> 00:15:02.984
(Pljesak)